Bharti Airtel, Ecobank Sign Agreement on Mobile Banking Services in Africa

-- B y   E m e l e   O n u
-- 
2011-06-06T16:07:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/ecobank-bharti-airtel-sign-agreement-to-promote-mobile-banking-in-africa.html
Ecobank Transational Inc. and  Bharti
Airtel Ltd. (BHARTI)  signed a memorandum of understanding to boost mobile
banking services across  Africa , Ecobank said.  “Both companies will launch a wide range of mobile
financial services offerings,” Lome, Togo-based Ecobank,
Africa’s largest lender by geographical spread, said in an-
emailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emele Onu in Johannesburg at 
 eonu1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  